= SDL_Delay =
Use this function to wait a specified number of milliseconds before returning.


== Syntax ==
```c++
void SDL_Delay(Uint32 ms)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''ms'''
|the number of milliseconds to delay (32-bit)
|}

